* Mini HV power-MOSFET fixture (E2E finding A2/A4/A3).
* A bare .model VDMOS and a 3-node subckt whose names collide on a prefix,
* mirroring the real corpus where --type mosfet hid the subckt-form HV part.
.model IRFTEST01 VDMOS (VTO=4 KP=20)
* IR-convention N-Channel Power MOS-FET
*SRC=IRFTEST;IRFTEST;MOSFETs N;Power >100V;400V 10A
.subckt IRFTEST 10 20 30
m1 10 20 30 30 IRFTEST01
.ends
